{
  "stem": "23428.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, in fact, you know, while I was disassembling airplanes and building roads and this sort of thing, other people, in fact, worked in textile factories and in the coal mines, as I mentioned already, a number of industrial outfits that, you know, where the mechanism was always set by the-- by truck full.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You were shipped out in the morning to-- to your work, to your work detail.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that started at maybe 5:00 in the morning and went on till late at night.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Very little sleep, and obviously, one ladle full of rather watery soup, maybe a piece of bread every day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They're not useful to the-- to the Reich anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A very [? rational ?] operation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At least that, I think, was the principle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In fact, they did, of course, send all of these guys to-- to death, once your-- your bones were sticking out, and you obviously couldn't work anymore.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, I was never in that category, obviously, for obvious reasons because that time was long-- not long enough.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my previous conditions was too good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then also, I had this absence of an A on my arm, which helped.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I also knew Prussian manners-- I mean, how to walk by the SS officers in a erect fashion and self-confident fashion.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That-- that-- that played also a large role, you know, because all in theory, this institution existed to weed out Muselmanns.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I am convinced that if you look by the criteria of the SS, particularly Jewish, your chances were much augmented of being gassed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got a ladle of soup in the evening.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or two, in my case, when I was a nurse, right.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
